<ooo title="mod_highlight" path="/projects/apache/mod_highlight/" osi="on">
 <section title="Abstract">
    <content type="docbook">
      <para>
        mod_highlight provdes syntax highlighting as an Apache 2.0 Filter Module. By Embeding the 
        <ulink url="http://colorer.sourceforge.net/">Colorer-Take5</ulink> library the module can process
        just about any programing language.
      </para>
    </content>
 </section>

